      "name": "List 5",
      "chunk_text": "Mode contract: (1) `markdown` default SSOT, (2) `html` view-only iframe, (3) `json` view-only iframe.\n`markdown`: editor/viewer use Markdown (graph parsing remains aligned to Markdown)\n`html`: editor stays editable Markdown SSOT; viewer/presentation/slides render sandboxed HTML via iframe `srcdoc`\n`json`: editor shows conversion JSON (read-only override); viewer/presentation/slides render sandboxed JSON via iframe `srcdoc`",
      "properties": {
        "order": 5
      },
