      "labels": [
        "List"
      ],
      "name": "List 1",
      "chunk_text": "`chatProvider` defaults to BytePlus ModelArk (`ap-southeast-1`) with OpenAI as the secondary official profile; preserve canonical official endpoint URLs in Settings even though requests route through the same-origin proxy.\n`chatAuthMode` selects `serverManaged` (default) vs `byok`.",
