      "name": "In Chat UI with `chatStorageTarget=chatKnowgrph`, `New Chat` creates a fresh `kg",
      "chunk_text": "In Chat UI with `chatStorageTarget=chatKnowgrph`, `New Chat` creates a fresh `kgc_yyyymmddhhmmss.md`, opens it in Workspace Editor (markdown pane), clears the active chat thread, and routes the next request/response into that new file.",
      "properties": {
        "text": "In Chat UI with `chatStorageTarget=chatKnowgrph`, `New Chat` creates a fresh `kgc_yyyymmddhhmmss.md`, opens it in Workspace Editor (markdown pane), clears the active chat thread, and routes the next request/response into that new file.",
