      "name": "`chatKnowgrph` validation and correction retries are handled upstream through th",
      "chunk_text": "`chatKnowgrph` validation and correction retries are handled upstream through the existing submit helpers and validator/recovery modules; malformed wrapped output may be salvaged before validation, but only the canonical recovered KGC document is persisted and applied.",
      "properties": {
        "text": "`chatKnowgrph` validation and correction retries are handled upstream through the existing submit helpers and validator/recovery modules; malformed wrapped output may be salvaged before validation, but only the canonical recovered KGC document is persisted and applied.",
