      "name": "Paragraph 2",
      "chunk_text": "**Intent**: Let users configure Gemini Veo video generation parameters (model, aspect ratio, resolution, duration, person generation) with safe defaults and localStorage persistence.",
      "properties": {
        "text": "**Intent**: Let users configure Gemini Veo video generation parameters (model, aspect ratio, resolution, duration, person generation) with safe defaults and localStorage persistence.",
